  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a cataplana over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and minced garlic, sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in smoked paprika and tomato paste, cooking for 1 minute.",
    "Deglaze with white wine, allowing the alcohol to evaporate.",
    "Pour in fish stock and bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add chopped kimchi and simmer for 3 minutes to warm through.",
    "Place cod fillets into the pot, cover, and simmer for 10 minutes until cooked.",
    "Sprinkle fresh cilantro, adjust seasoning, and serve hot."
